Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:04.46,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,德勒韦斯大人怎么会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.14,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.89,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,火焰风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.35,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我来开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.06,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:04.05,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,好 长势不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.85,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们开始下一个阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.87,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,可以用这片地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.45,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 领主大人已经同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.28,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:15.92,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.13,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,刚才那个就是圣女之术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.55,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.79,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,刚才那个就是圣女之术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.15,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你已经可以自由使用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.19,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过你为什么要在这种地方使用…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.89,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,更重要的是为什么不在我面前使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.15,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,欺负我吗？还是说故意使坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:48.95,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:53.25,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是我想要练习一下魔法 所以她带我来了这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.17,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.67,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这边才刚刚准备好 还什么都没有种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:03.30,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣女之术也不会对田地有危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.61,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:10.83,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过虽说没有危害 可对土地说不定有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.45,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.61,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,能感觉到奇特的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.24,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,能判断出有什么样的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.77,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.63,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,要么魔力会滞留在土地中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.98,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,要么就是矿物会被附魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.23,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,两种情况都有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.49,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在也就是假设阶段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:36.00,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,要仔细验证一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.24,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.66,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这两人聊得怪开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.96,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们开始下一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.94,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:46.52,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.95,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:54.97,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.17,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.36,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:11.16,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,看来圣女之术会消耗大量的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.69,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.88,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.82,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,结果还是让我连续用了好几次…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.94,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,反复练习才能掌握好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:27.40,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,以后还得多加练习 提升发动魔法的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.38,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？还…还要更快吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.79,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那是不是有点…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:37.04,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,发动魔法之前我需要不少准备的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.52,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.86,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,说起来发动的条件是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.78,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.13,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.02,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不好说出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.11,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这样吗 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.04,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,诶？这就算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.11,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,难道你愿意说出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.06,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.21,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:06.62,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.12,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.67,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,打搅了 我听说你在这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:15.44,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不用在意 你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.10,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,讨伐队伍重新编排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.80,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,希望你确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.08,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣也一起确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.70,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我这边没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.08,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.28,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,史莱姆吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.56,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,有点等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.10,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣小姐 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.11,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,爱良 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.35,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们好像是一队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:57.05,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吧 爱良也要参与进攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.91,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,估计是要看情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.42,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过我基本上是负责治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.40,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,因为前辈说团长大概不会参与治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.12,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.89,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,早上好 圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.32,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:15.69,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.29,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,莱昂先生也和我们一队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.00,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.68,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,早上好 圣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.48,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.13,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.70,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,他就是灰烬恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:30.51,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.14,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,某次大规模讨伐任务中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.81,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,他将怪物连同周围的一切都燃烧殆尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以就有了这么个外号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.49,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,希望他能控制住自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:43.72,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.35,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,希望这次任务的森林没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.73,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.82,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,得提前拜托他别引燃森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.07,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,冰矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.66,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,范围守护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.01,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:17.59,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.28,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,姑娘 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:23.10,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣女大人 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.43,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.69,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,怪物的数量增多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.39,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,史莱姆的数量也变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.38,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,说不定离那沼泽不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,德勒韦斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.71,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 爱护森林是吧 我没忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.35,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,怪物出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.38,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,迎敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.25,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,数量太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.43,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,保持警戒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.56,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.16,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,保持阵型！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.25,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.89,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,水墙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.22,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,冰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.24,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,冰墙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.21,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,地刺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.64,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:49.70,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.41,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.23,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.91,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,还不是时候 火矛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.26,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.07,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.33,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.47,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.66,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.73,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:26.72,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,只是圣女之术消耗的魔力过多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.44,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,在找到沼泽之前希望你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:43.92,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.95,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人 从这个位置可以净化到黑色沼泽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.92,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,能…能不能靠近一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.96,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了 我想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:25.59,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不管怎样我们现在也无法撤退 只有前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.71,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,准备上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.99,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.05,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,全员冲锋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.14,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,电团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.20,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.50,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:02.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.18,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.30,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.44,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:32.31,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们来对付史莱姆 圣大人专注发动魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.04,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.13,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.04,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,业火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.49,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.43,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.69,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间 必须抓紧时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.37,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.26,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 只是在发呆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.23,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗 今天很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.98,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你也累了吧 早些休息比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.33,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢团长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:04.88,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:09.50,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那我就先休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.49,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.31,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:14.46,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.88,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:27.64,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不必在意 那你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.78,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.16,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.05,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你是不是有什么心事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.77,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白 再要求更多就有些任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:04.73,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是 我还是无法就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:12.53,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣 我是王国的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.87,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的剑就是王的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.34,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,可如果可能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.39,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也希望成为守护你的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:27.15,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,能否让我实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.67,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.67,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那…那个 那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:29.12,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,要专心 专心…专心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.62,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:38.85,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不是…你一直盯着我 我不好集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.76,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你请便 不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.19,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,真的可以做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.29,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.31,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.36,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,愿森林恢复生机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.04,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.46,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,好厉害 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:24.17,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这是…克劳斯纳的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.27,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣？圣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.45,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:44.95,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:45.46,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.39,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.77,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,为…为什么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.52,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你是累坏了吧 突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.55,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我真的没事了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.59,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,这是你让我们担心的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.32,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.49,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,我想自己走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.58,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:56.93,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,那至少能让我陪伴着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:19:59.74,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.90,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:15.60,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没有 我才是得到了不少帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:19.89,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,你不在了 药水制作又不容易了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.54,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:26.71,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么不至于 只有你能制作那么多药水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:33.21,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过正如领主大人所说 你就是我们的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.17,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.76,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,哟！准备回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:37.77,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.27,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.17,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,莱昂先生也多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:45.18,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 王都待烦了随时可以来这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:50.12,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,说什么呢 交给你还不如让她来我这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.16,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.32,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.22,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的帮助和照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.65,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:06.70,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣女的魔力还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.19,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,竟然连森林都再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:10.73,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.27,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过她的厉害之处不只是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.38,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,其实我们都拥有那样的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.72,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,啊？老太你一把年纪 人傻了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.07,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.78,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,不是什么复杂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.72,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣女的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.22,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,就是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.12,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,还是自己家最舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:15.58,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,过不了多久又会有新的讨伐任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.30,0:23:18.21,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,又要麻烦圣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:19.84,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:21.23,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:25.55,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 霍克大人不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.51,Dial-CHS,,0,0,0,,圣女的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.81,Title,,0,0,0,,「返回」
