Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.47,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Oh what a beautiful site
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.78,0:19:50.00,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I see your face beyond the curtain of clouds
