Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.07,0:19:58.44,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Your tenderness
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.52,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,2000)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I want to tell you everything about my day
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.01,0:20:10.06,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Especially when something good has happened
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.06,0:20:18.58,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}And if {\alpha&HFF&\t(4000,4400,\alpha&H00&)}I ever saw you down I’ll hold you tight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.54,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I won’t ever let go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.51,0:20:46.12,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}Because of you the sadness all disappears
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.19,0:20:50.49,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}The nights don’t seem so scary anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.86,0:20:58.65,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}And now in gracefulness my flower starts to bloom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.80,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}My heart skips a beat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.80,0:21:10.73,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}But it’s so hard to show what I’m feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.38,0:21:19.66,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}I just can’t help it somehow I say all the wrong words
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.85,0:21:22.09,OP2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur2\fad(480,480)\bord1\fscx90\fscy90}It’s funny, I know…
